Source: php-xml-beautifier
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Mathias Ertl <apt-repository@fsinf.at>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8), dh-make-php (>= 0.2.3), cdbs, php-pear (>=1.3.0)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1

Package: php-xml-beautifier
Architecture: all
Depends: php-pear, php-xml-parser (>= 1.0), ${misc:Depends} 
Description: Class to format XML documents.
 XML_Beautifier will add indentation and linebreaks to you XML
 files, replace all entities, format your comments and makes your
 document easier to read.  You can  influence the way your document
 is beautified with several options, ranging from indentation to
 changing the case of tags and normalizing your comments.
